Questions:
If you choose not to participate in providing information for the BMT CTN 1902 study, what alternative option is available to you for your usual health care?
A) You will be required to participate in a different clinical trial; 
B) You will not receive any medical care or advice for your pregnancy;
C) You can continue your usual health care without any changes;
D) You will be provided with a special counseling service for pregnancy-related issues.

Correct answer: C
